opencsg
------------------------------------------
OpenCSG is a library that does image-based CSG rendering using OpenGL.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.0-1
  libGL1-19.1.6-1
  libGLU1-9.0.2-1
  libgcc1-12.4.0-3
  libglut3-3.4.0-1
  libopencsg-devel-1.8.1-1bl1
  libopencsg1-1.8.1-1bl1
  libstdc++6-12.4.0-3
  pkg-config-2.3.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.44-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  gcc-g++-12.4.0-3
  libGL-devel-19.1.6-1
  libGLEW-devel-2.1.0-1
  libglut-devel-3.4.0-1
  ninja-1.12.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://www.opencsg.org/

Canonical download:
  https://www.opencsg.org/OpenCSG-1.8.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack opencsg-1.8.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./opencsg-1.8.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/opencsg-1.8.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/opencsg-1.8.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libopencsg1-1.8.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libopencsg-devel-1.8.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(opencsg)
  /usr/bin/opencsgexample.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/opencsg.README
  /usr/share/doc/opencsg/README.md
  /usr/share/doc/opencsg/changelog.txt
  /usr/share/doc/opencsg/copying.txt

(libopencsg1)
  /usr/bin/cygopencsg-1.dll

(libopencsg-devel)
  /usr/include/opencsg.h
  /usr/lib/libopencsg.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/opencsg.pc

